{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-verb}}\n\n# {{lb|fr|informal|figurative}} to have the [[blues]], to [[feel]] [[blue]]\n#: {{ux|fr|Il fait du soleil aujourd'hui, mais j''''ai le cafard'''.|It's sunny today, but I '''feel blue'''.}}\n#: {{ux|fr|Elle vient d'être licenciée, c'est normal d''''avoir le cafard'''.|She has just been fired, it's normal to '''feel blue'''.}}\n#* {{quote-song\n|fr\n|composer=Jean Éblinger\n|title=J'ai l'cafard\n|artist=w:Fréhel\n|year=1927\n|passage=J''''ai l'cafard''', j''''ai l'cafard''' / Je le sens qui me perce comme avec un poignard / La cervelle d'part en part\n|t=I '''have the blues''', I '''am feeling blue''' / I feel it piercing me like a dagger / Brains through and through}}\n\n====Conjugation====\n* see {{m|fr|avoir}}\n\n","alt":[],"syn":[],"type":"verb","forms":[{"mod":"inf","aux":["avoir"],"pronom":false}],"html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/avoir#French\" title=\"avoir\">avoir</a> <a href=\"/wiki/le#French\" title=\"le\">le</a> <a href=\"/wiki/cafard#French\" title=\"cafard\">cafard</a></strong></span>\n</p><ol><li><span class=\"usage-label-sense\"><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content label-content\"><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#informal\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">informal</a><span class=\"ib-comma label-comma\">,</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#figurative\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">figurative</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">)</span></span> to have the <a href=\"/wiki/blues\" title=\"blues\">blues</a>, to <a href=\"/wiki/feel\" title=\"feel\">feel</a> <a href=\"/wiki/blue\" title=\"blue\">blue</a>\n<dl><dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Il fait du soleil aujourd'hui, mais j'<b>ai le cafard</b>.</i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">It's sunny today, but I <b>feel blue</b>.</span></dd></dl></div></dd>\n<dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Elle vient d'être licenciée, c'est normal d'<b>avoir le cafard</b>.</i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">She has just been fired, it's normal to <b>feel blue</b>.</span></dd></dl></div></dd></dl>\n<ul><li><div class=\"citation-whole\"><span class=\"cited-source\"><span class=\"None\" lang=\"und\"><b>1927</b></span>, “J'ai l'cafard”, Jean Éblinger (music), performed by <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fr%C3%A9hel\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Fréhel\">Fréhel</a>:</span><dl><dd><div class=\"h-quotation\"><span class=\"Latn e-quotation cited-passage\" lang=\"fr\">J'<b>ai l'cafard</b>, j'<b>ai l'cafard</b> / Je le sens qui me perce comme avec un poignard / La cervelle d'part en part</span><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">I <b>have the blues</b>, I <b>am feeling blue</b> / I feel it piercing me like a dagger / Brains through and through</span></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></div></li></ul></li></ol><div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading4\"><h4 id=\"Conjugation\">Conjugation</h4><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=avoir_le_cafard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Conjugation\"><span>edit</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></div>","trans":["to have the blues, to feel blue"]}],"title":"avoir le cafard","id":"192952","audios":[{"name":"LL-Q150 (fra)-LoquaxFR-avoir le cafard.wav","url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/74/LL-Q150_%28fra%29-LoquaxFR-avoir_le_cafard.wav"}],"ipas":["/a.vwaʁ lə ka.faʁ/"],"pronunSection":"\n* {{fr-IPA}}\n* {{audio|fr|LL-Q150 (fra)-LoquaxFR-avoir le cafard.wav}}\n\n","pronunHtml":"<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:International_Phonetic_Alphabet\" title=\"Wiktionary:International Phonetic Alphabet\">IPA</a><sup>(<a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:French_pronunciation\" title=\"Appendix:French pronunciation\">key</a>)</sup>: <span class=\"IPA\">/a.vwaʁ lə ka.faʁ/</span></li>\n<li><style data